xy \in (x^2,y^2)R
x,y
R
(x_{1}\ldots x_{n+1})^{n} \in (x_{1}^{n+1}, \ldots,x_{n+1}^{n+1})R
R
(x) = \prod_{i} P^{\alpha_i}_i
(y) = \prod_i P^{\beta_i}_i
(x^2, y^2) = \prod_i P^{\min\{2\alpha_i, 2\beta_i\}}_i = \prod_i P^{2\min\{\alpha_i, \beta_i\}}_i
(xy) = \prod_i P^{\alpha_i + \beta_i}_i
\alpha_i + \beta_i \geq 2\min\{\alpha_i, \beta_i\}
(xy) \subset (x^2,y^2)
